              <lb n="1"/>Di<hi rend="tall">i</hi>s Manibus.
              <lb n="2"/><persName><name type="gentilicium" key="Aufustiae">Aufustiae</name> <name type="cognomen" key="Hedone">Hedone</name></persName>; vixit
              <lb n="3"/>annis <num type="cardinal" value="90">LXXXX</num>. Fecit
              <lb n="4"/><persName><name type="gentilicium" key="Aufustia">Aufustia</name> <g type="mulieris"/> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>iberta</ex></expan> <name type="cognomen" key="Stratonice">Stratonice</name></persName>
              <lb n="5"/>libertis libertabus <expan><abbr>posterisq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan>
              <lb n="6"/>eorum. In <expan><abbr>fr</abbr><ex>onte</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> <num type="cardinal" value="12">XII</num>, in <expan><abbr>agr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> <num type="cardinal" value="16">XVI</num>.
           </ab>
         </div>
        
        
                <div type="translation">
                    <p>To the divine spirits. To Aufustia Hedone; she lived for ninety years. Aufustia Stratonice, the freedwoman of a woman, made this for (her and her) freedmen and freedwomen and their descendants. The plot is twelve feet wide, and sixteen feet deep.</p>
                </div>
            
        
        
